{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876784098,"sessionID":"ses_28580d662ffeyNGTIvNO1GV5Sf","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7f3408001mtGUj0nkPpMr71","messageID":"msg_d7a7f2a93001koKmw2JR6DGNvI","sessionID":"ses_28580d662ffeyNGTIvNO1GV5Sf","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_a92700874c364580ac5e76ce","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to understand:\n1. Project structure (top-level directories and key files)\n2. Whether there's an existing Makefile or any build system\n3. Any existing spec files (delta-spec.md, spec.md, etc.) to understand the format used\n4. What the project does (look at README, package.json, or similar)\n5. Any existing OpenSpec or spec-related files in the project\n6. Look for any opsx/ or specs/ directories\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of findings including file paths and relevant content snippets.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_28580b9b9ffeKBJmda9nrMy46g (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the AgentCube project:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Project Summary: AgentCube\n\n### 1. Project Structure (Top-Level Directories and Key Files)\n\n**Root directory:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`\n\n| Entry | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `cmd/` | dir | Go binaries: `agentd/`, `cli/`, `picod/`, `router/`, `workloadmanager/` |\n| `pkg/` | dir | Go packages: `agentd/`, `apis/`, `common/`, `picod/`, `router/`, `store/`, `workloadmanager/` |\n| `changes/` | dir | 33 change requests (AR-001 through AR-033), each with delta-spec.md, design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | dir | CLI spec and design files |\n| `python-sdk/` | dir | Python SDK spec and design files |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | dir | Sandbox