oml` in `sdk-python/`) for the Python SDK\n- **Helm 3** for Kubernetes packaging (under `manifests/charts/`)\n- **Docker** multi-stage builds (under `docker/`)\n- **GitHub Actions** for CI/CD (referenced in `project.md`)\n\n### 3. Existing Spec Files and Format\n\nThe project uses a **rich spec-driven development (SDD)** methodology with multiple spec file types:\n\n#### Spec File Types Found:\n\n| File Pattern | Count | Purpose |\n|-------------|-------|---------|\n| `delta-spec.md` | 27 files (root + 26 in `changes/AR-XXX/`) | Incremental/delta specs for individual change requests |\n| `spec.md` | 11 files (in feature directories) | Full feature specifications |\n| `design.md` | Multiple | Technical design documents |\n| `proposal.md` | Multiple | Change request proposals with alternatives analysis |\n| `tasks.md` | Multiple | Task breakdowns with dependency graphs |\n\n#### Spec Format (from `delta-spec.md` and `spec.md`):\n\nThe spec format uses **Gherkin-style Given/When/Then scenarios** with RFC 2119 normative language (SHALL/SHOULD/MAY).\n\n**Example structure from `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md`:**\n```markdown\n# AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n- **Module:** `sdk-python`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n\n## Scope\n[Description of what the delta spec covers]\n\n---\n\n## HTTP Session Factory\n\n### Requirement: create_session\nThe system SHALL provide a `create_session` function...\n\n#### Scenario: default pool parameters\n- **GIVEN** `create_session()` is called with no arguments\n- **WHEN** the session is created\n- **THEN** `HTTPAdapter(pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)` SHALL be mounted...\n```\n\n**Example from a feature-level spec (`sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`):**\n```markdown\n# Sandbox Orchestration Specification\n\n## Purpose\nOrchestrate agent sandboxes via Kubernetes CRDs...\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD schema and API registration\nThe system SHALL expose a namespaced `AgentRuntime` custom resource...\n\n#### Scenario: Group version and resource naming\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes API client resolving the CRD\n- **WHEN** the group, version, and kind are read from type metadata\n- **THEN** `GroupVersion` is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`...\n```\n\n#### Change Request Directory Structure (e.g., `changes/AR-033/`):\nEach AR (Agent Request) directory contains exactly 4 files:\n- `delta-spec.md` -- Incremental specification\n- `design.md` -- Technical design\n- `proposal.md` -- Proposal with alternatives analysis\n- `tasks.md` -- Task breakdown with dependency graph\n\n### 4. What the Project Does\n\n**AgentCube** is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents**. Key capabilities:\n\n- **Provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand** via Kubernetes CRDs (`AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`)\n- **Routes HTTP traffic** to sandbox pods through session-aware proxies (Router component)\n- **Manages sandbox lifecycle**: creation, expiry, idle cleanup\n- **Provides a Python SDK** (`agentcube-sdk`) with `CodeInterpreterClient` and `AgentRuntimeClient`\n- **Provides a CLI tool** (`kubectl-agentcube`) for packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and checking status of AI agents\n- **Includes a code execution daemon** (PicoD) for running code inside sandboxes\n- **Supports session persistence** via Redis/Valkey\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n- **Server (Go):** Go 1.24/1.25, Gin HTTP framework, controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox`\n- **CLI/SDK (Python):** Python >= 3.10, Typer (CLI), requests (SDK)\n- **Kubernetes:** CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`)\n- **Storage:** Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go)\n- **Auth:** JWT RS256, K8s TokenReview\n- **Packaging:** Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions\n\n### 5. Existing OpenSpec or Spec-Related Files\n\n- **`project.md`** at root: Titled \"AgentCube -- OpenSpec Project Context\" -- explicitly references OpenSpec methodology\n- **`delta-spec.md`** at root: AR-029 delta spec\n- **`test_spec.md`** at root: TDD specification\n- **`/changes/AR-XXX/delta-spec.md`**: 26 delta specs for individual change requests\n- **Feature-level `spec.md`** files in: `sandbox-orchestration/`, `python-sdk/`, `cli-toolkit/`, `code-execution/`, `session-routing/`, `session-store/`, `ci-cd/`, `idle-cleanup/`, `deployment/`, `integrations/`\n- **`.sdd_prompt.md`**: Spec-Driven Development prompt template used to generate design documents\n\n### 6. opsx/ or specs/ Directories\n\n**Neither `opsx/` nor `specs/` directories exist** in the project. Both glob searches returned no results.\n\nThe closest equivalents are:\n- `changes/` -- Contains all change request artifacts (delta-specs, designs, proposals, tasks)\n- Feature directories with embedded `spec.md` files (e.g., `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`)\n\n---\n\n### Key File Paths Summary\n\n| Purpose | Absolute Path |\n|---------|---------------|\n| Project context | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` |\n| Go module definition | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod` |\n| Root delta spec (AR-029) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` |\n| Root design doc (AR-029) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` |\n| Root proposal (AR-028) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` |\n| Root tasks (AR-023) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` |\n| TDD spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` |\n| SDD prompt | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` |\n| Makefile delta spec (AR-033, stub) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md` |\n| Sandbox orchestration spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` |\n| Python SDK spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md` |\n| CLI toolkit spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md` |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28580b9b9ffeKBJmda9nrMy46g","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775876654659,"end":1775876784095}}}}
